Package: ascendo
Source: ubuntu-aktualizacje
Version: 0.3.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 5.0), python3 (>= 3.11), python3-venv, git, util-linux, sudo, apt
Recommends: timeshift | etckeeper, snapd, fwupd, libsecret-tools
Maintainer: Mateusz Kasprowicz <gaipro.mk@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/KasprowiczM/Ubuntu_Aktualizacje
Description: One-command Ubuntu system update manager with dashboard
 Ubuntu_Aktualizacje is a hybrid CLI + local FastAPI dashboard that drives
 a 5-phase per-category update pipeline (apt, snap, brew, npm, pip,
 flatpak, drivers, inventory). Each run emits structured JSON sidecars
 (schema v1) so the state of every update is auditable. Includes
 single-prompt sudo, live progress, snapshot integration (timeshift /
 etckeeper), Prometheus /metrics, and Markdown report export.
